# 2.6 Scope of the Project

The implemented system covers the following capabilities.

## University Discovery

Identify leading universities for a given course and country.

Example:

- Artificial Intelligence
- Machine Learning
- Data Science
- Computer Science

---

## Scholarship Information

Retrieve scholarship opportunities associated with:

- Universities
- Countries
- Academic programs

---

## Cost of Living

