- Rent
- Food
- Transportation
- Miscellaneous costs

---

## Visa Guidance

Provide information such as:

- Student visa type
- Required documents
- Processing timelines
- Work permissions

---

## Geographic Context

Enrich recommendations with:

- Current weather
- Nearby attractions
- Campus surroundings

---

## Report Generation

Generate a structured Markdown report summarizing all retrieved information.

